name: "RIPYT"
description:
****these prints will not be available just yet, i started printing them the other day, but ran into some issues with one of the colors, and unfortunately could not get the problem fixed before i left for tour. i will hopefully have the problem fixed asap and have them up. keep checking for updates. im sorry for the delay, hopefully everyone can understand. i only had 3 days at home before tour. lots of stuff to do.****

"RIPYT" was created in honor of the recently passed King of Pop - Michael Jackson. He was an amazing musician that inspired many. RIP MJ. 

All profits will be donated to the Worcester Public School Music Program.

19x25, 3 Color, Hand Screen Printed Poster.

Limited to only 50 posters. 

Designed and prited by Alan Day of DEATHorGLORY.
